== Familichi Bhett Magnnem ==
'''Family Prayer'''


Eh ojeapanche Ankvari, sorpott poddun Tujea Imaji mhukar, 

ami aileanv ekanne bhettounk Tuje chakrek, amcho jiv, 

amcheam kalliz, amcheam ghordar, amcho vavr-dhondo ani 

sogllem amchem lagim asa tem Tuka bhettoitanv. 

Besanv ghal he familicher ji sodta dakhounk 

Tuzo mog korta mhonn; besanv ghal heam bhurgeancher, 

sambhalunk tim nitoll ani nirmoll; besanv ghal amcheam 

putam-dhuvancher, aplea bhavartan ani xegunnanim zoit, 

tannim vhorunk sonvsaracheam perigancher ani aplea 

otmeacheam dusmanacher, besanv ghal avoi bapaicher, 

tannim favo te porim pallunk aple kaide, besanv 

ghal amcher sogleancher, Tuje vorvim tankunk ami 

sodanch vatt Sorginchi, Povitr Arluk zaunk amchea 

jivachi rakhonn ani bhangarachi chavi ugddunk amkam 

dharam Sorginchim 

''Oxem Zaun.'' 


'''''Amen'''''


